title: NFL Week Two Previews, Eagles' Lane Johnson, Pigskin Picks, and Nate Burleson
itunes:title: NFL Week Two Previews, Eagles' Lane Johnson, Pigskin Picks, and Nate Burleson
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Cris Carter get ready for NFL Week Two! The Mad Minute brings the best games of the weekend. Eagles OT Lane Johnson explains how the team is preparing for the 49ers. Kay gives her Top Five Friday fantasy football picks. Nate Burleson talks about comparisons to Michael Strahan plus the Pigskin Picks!
